<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Panel de Control - Aldea Vikinga</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap"
          rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        /* --- ESTILOS GENERALES Y FONDO --- */
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; /* Fuente legible para textos */
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            /* IMAGEN DE FONDO: Trama de escudos sutil */
            /* He usado un placeholder que simula madera oscura con textura */
            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/dark-wood.png');
            background-repeat: repeat;
        }

        h1, h2, th, .btn-add {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; /* Fuente épica para títulos */
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* --- CABECERA ÉPICA (HEADER) --- */
        header {
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(26, 26, 26, 1)),
            url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578130325150-f70915a7702a?q=80&w=1600'); /* Placeholder Drakkar */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 300px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #d4af37; /* Línea dorada */
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        header h1 {
            color: #d4af37; /* Oro viejo */
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin: 0;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }

        header p {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* --- CONTENEDOR PRINCIPAL --- */
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: -50px auto 50px auto; /* Sube un poco para pisar el header */
            background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.95);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            border: 1px solid #444;
            position: relative; /* Para el z-index */
        }

        /* --- BOTÓN DE ALTA (RECLUTAR) --- */
        .btn-add {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #c0392b; /* Rojo sangre fuerte */
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            border: 2px solid #a93226;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-add:hover {
            background-color: #d4af37; /* Cambia a Oro al pasar el mouse */
            color: #1a1a1a;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* --- TABLA VIKINGA --- */
        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #262626;
            border: 2px solid #d4af37; /* Borde dorado tabla */
        }

        th, td {
            padding: 18px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #444;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #d4af37;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #d4af37;
        }

        tr:hover {
            background-color: #333; /* Resalta fila */
        }

        /* Icono de fuerza (hacha) */
        .fuerza-icon {
            color: #d4af37;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        /* --- BOTONES DE ACCIÓN DENTRO DE TABLA --- */
        .actions a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin-right: 5px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .edit {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #3498db;
            border: 1px solid #3498db;
        }

        .edit:hover {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
        }

        .delete {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #e74c3c;
            border: 1px solid #e74c3c;
        }

        .delete:hover {
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
        }

        /* --- FORMULARIOS --- */
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            color: #d4af37;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .form-group input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            background-color: #2a2a2a;
            border: 1px solid #555;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 1em;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }

        .form-group input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #d4af37;
        }

        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #c0392b;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            background-color: #d4af37;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }

        .back-link {
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #888;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            color: #d4af37;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Salón del Trono</h1>
    <p>"AQUÍ SE FORJAN LAS LEYENDAS QUE CANTARÁN LOS SKALDOS"</p>
</header>